Ports are fixed and non-negotiable.
Frontend MUST run on localhost:3000 (FRONTEND_PORT=3000).
Backend MUST run on localhost:4000 (BACKEND_PORT=4000).
Read ports only from .env.
Do not assume defaults or auto-increment ports.
Fail if the port is unavailable.
Start services only via package.json scripts.